            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "通向未来的大门只会为\\n有决心做出选择的人敞开！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "士兵A",
            "context": "我、我相信你的话！\\n我还不想死！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "士兵B",
            "context": "没错，我怎么能死在这里。\\n我还要回去见家人呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "人类和龙，\\n现在团结一致了……",
