            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "咦，这些光是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这些都是祈祷……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "全世界的人们的祈祷\\n将魔力带到了这里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "他们将魔力托付给我……\\n那么我该做的就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "作为巫女\\n将祈祷和魔力结合在一起，\\n再将更多的光集中到这里！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "丰沃的魔力啊，赐予我力量，\\n带给我想要的未来吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我叫塞西娅，\\n乃被神圣魔力选中之人。\\n现对所有魔力进行引导！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "魔力回应了塞西娅的召唤。\\n这就是塞西娅的力量吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "回应祈祷，化为一道光吧。\\n驱除灾厄，还大地以安宁！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "多么神圣的光芒啊……\\n真是惊人的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（哥哥……一直以来\\n我都被你保护着。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（但是这次……换我来保护你。\\n保护大家都在的未来！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "刚才，听到了塞西娅的声音……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "我也听到了。\\n但这怎么可能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。塞西娅被神秘男子掳走……\\n目前行踪不明，\\n怎么可能听到她的声音。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是，如果不光是我，\\n连纳姆也听见了的话……\\n感觉就不是幻听。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "嗯……塞西娅\\n她现在在哪里呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不知道。现在我们能做的，\\n就是为了夺回塞西娅而奋勇前行。\\n还有就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "纳姆，\\n你愿意和我一起祈祷吗？\\n祈祷塞西娅能平安无事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "嗯，是啊。我们一起祈祷吧。\\n祈祷塞西娅能平安无事。\\n祈祷我们还能再见到她。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_10_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
